---
title: Middle Eastern Chicken with spinach and pine nut bulgur wheat
description: This hearty and decadent chicken stew is filled with flavours from the Middle East. Harissa, bulgur wheat and lentils are all ingredients commonly found in many of this region's cuisines.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF221122_R12_W03_IE_IEQCLC13090-2_MB_Main_high-0605ca0e.jpg
